metadata.name: Who looks Inside, Awakes!
metadata.description:
“Your vision will become clear only when you can look into your own heart. Who looks Outside, Dreams; Who looks Inside, Awakes.” ~ Carl Jung

1/1 Digital Abstract Work

Resolution: 4500px*4500px

800 dpi

Format: PNG (a PNG and a JPEG image of upto 8000px*8000px and 800 dpi would be made available upon request)

No AI has been used in the creation of any of my digital art works.
